title: DC Nation's Farm League
overview: DC Nation's Farm League is a series of shorts based around the adventures of the Justice League of Animals and its members Supermanatee, Wonder Wombat, Cybug, Aquamandrill, Batmongoose, Robin's Egg, The Flish, Ambush Slug and Shazham. Fighting villains like Sinestropotamus, Cat Cat, Moo-Face, Croaker, Captain Cod, Lex Liger, and Duckseid.
